page_title: How to work with DALL-E models
page_description: Learn about the options for how to use the DALL-E image generation models.
chunk_content: Prerequisites#### DALL-E 3- An Azure subscription. Create one for free.- An Azure OpenAI resource created in the `SwedenCentral` region.- Then, you need to deploy a `dalle3` model with your Azure resource. For more information, see Create a resource and deploy a model with Azure OpenAI.#### DALL-E 2 (preview)- An Azure subscription. Create one for free.- An Azure OpenAI resource created in the East US region. For more information, see Create a resource and deploy a model with Azure OpenAI.---
